message: A pony fell out of an animal trailer and was dragged by its neck! 

The owner of a mobile petting zoo in Phoenix, Arizona faces animal cruelty charges after a pony fell out of a makeshift animal trailer last week and was dragged by its neck until the driver finally realized what had happened and stopped:

